posts.body: If anyone was able to get this complete set, could you reupload it? Only like 7 or 8 seeded for me, the rest are in rotating circle limbo. I've even deleted Zeronet, including regedit, redownloaded Zeronet and still the same thing, only 7 or 8 will seed.

>>569fe510-6766-4752-9e4f-33ef54b54fe4
Np, thanks for sharing

>>6c57af3a-aa90-49ed-a88d-f82753f83c28
Just mute him, there used to be an option to blacklist individuals, I don't know what happened to that. Hopefully muting them will also prevent them from seeing your posts like blacklisting did. He probably just wants to be the first to upload the set to Thothub for them cool points. Those asshats are the real pandemic.

>>0fac19f9-336f-4068-8177-7923558f40f3
Fantastic, dude probably spends to much time on 4chan. We, the quiet majority, appreciate you and all the other uploaders.

>>39c9c372-6301-4691-a8e8-f87be6d12e39
Well it's definitely you bud, set was posted 8:24 this morning, I grabbed it around 10. Sooooooooo, maybe you just suck at life?
lol! This dude is obviously from 4chan! No one here gives a shit about your pity parade. Unlike 4chan though, here we can make you disappear, Buh Byeeee!
Nice, this was a upgrade, thanks.
Love this set, thanks!
I had this one in my To be Sorted Later Folder, haven't a clue where I got it but it's HQ.
Why have 3 different posts of the same set doh? What was wrong with Some Guy's post?

>>8eef5b82-3966-4bdb-8962-110b14017066
Your first post worked just fine for me.

You can also remove your other posts by clicking the little arrow.

>>d05bd4aa-83cf-4071-ac4f-d8eb8c817f2a
Oh wow, so it wasn't Thothub? Nigri released these images this small? The original set is like 5200x7200 and 16mb. Wonder why she compressed them so much.

>>3d061051-456a-4fe5-a636-15b5d086f949
I think he was implying that this set was taken off Thothub... they're an exact match to the set posted directly to Thothub, which by now we all know compresses images. If this person actually bought the set himself, they wouldn't be the same resolution as the ones posted on Thothub.
By far her best... a little weird considering the subject, but definitely does what it's supposed to. Thanks for the share!
Is she still relevant?
3 posts in a year? Why would you think she wasn't relevant?

>>1ae8bddb-0b29-48e9-9ace-953990d934e3
No one said she wasn't posting the same 5 second, different bikini, clip everyday. Just asking if she is relevant. Who knew posting the exact same thing everyday but with a different color bikini would get stale.

>>91c8a001-0edb-47ad-b298-58cb1498e071
Yeah, it was instant regret, low resolution and it looks like the pics were taken from a motorola razr.
